NexusOS GPL/LGPL Source Offer
=============================

Corresponding source for GPL and LGPL components included in NexusOS release
artifacts is available as follows:

1. **Debian packages** — run `apt source <package-name>` on a NexusOS system, or
   retrieve sources from https://snapshot.debian.org for the Debian release used
   at build time.

2. **Asahi Linux platform** (Apple Silicon) — https://github.com/AsahiLinux

3. **NexusOS-authored packages** — https://github.com/Aidiotic/Operating-system

4. **Written offer** — source requests may be submitted via GitHub Issues:
   https://github.com/Aidiotic/Operating-system/issues

A per-release package manifest (`SOURCES-{VERSION}.txt`) is published alongside
tagged releases when available.

**Draft — counsel review required:** This engineering notice is not a final
GPL §3 compliance determination. Obtain qualified legal review before broad
binary redistribution.
